Class Table

  • java.lang.Object
    • Class.Table
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Table
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This is a table class. It represents the table that the restaurant has. It implements serializable to allow us to serialize and deserialize to a file (Table.dat)
